verbose_text: We discover that two different HS modifying enzymes, Hs2st and Hs6st1, indeed differentially modulate the properties of emerging Fgf8 protein concentration gradients and the Erk signalling output in response to Fgf8 in living tissue in ex vivo cultures.
evidence: Hs6st1, indeed differentially modulate the properties of emerging Fgf8
